#, no-wrap
msgid "Data quality requirements for DNA reference libraries"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-publishing/modules/ROOT/pages/data-quality-recommendations.adoc:171
msgid ""
"Publishers who wish to share DNA reference libraries with GBIF must publish "
"them as https://github.com/gbif/tech-docs/edit/main/en/data-publishing/"
"modules/ROOT/pages/data-quality-recommendations.adoc#data-quality-"
"requirements-for-occurrences[occurrences] with the https://rs.gbif.org/"
"extension/gbif/1.0/dna_derived_data_2024-07-11.xml[DNA-derived data "
"extension]. A DNA reference library is any curated or computationally "
"assembled collection of taxonomically annotated DNA sequences, derived from "
"physical specimens or other biological sources, used as a basis for "
"identifying or classifying unknown biological material."
msgstr ""

